---
title: Bavarian Crispy Pork Belly & Braised Cabbage with Herby Apple Sauce, Creamy Mash & Gravy
description: Crispy pork belly is a staple in any Bavarian cafe, and we’re ready to be transported! This almighty protein is best enjoyed with an array of classic sides, including creamy potato mash, tangy braised cabbage and a sweet herby apple sauce. Dig in!
